FBIS4-6498 "dreas077_c_94047" FBIS-EAS-94-077 Daily Report 21 Apr 1994 North Korea Kim Il-song's Works Published, Reported Abroad Kim Il-song's Works Published, Reported Abroad SK2104110394 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1040 GMT 21 Apr 94 SK2104110394 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, April 21 (KCNA) -- The great leader President Kim Il-song's famous work "10-point Programme of the Great Unity of the Whole Nation for the Reunification of the Country" was published in booklet by the Kultura Publishing House of Yugoslavia, the National Publishing House of Laos, the Sofia Printing Combine of Bulgaria and the Litho Printing House of Tanzania. A detailed gist of the work was reported by the Burkinabe paper OBSERVATEUR, the Madagascan papers IMONGO VAOVAO and BASY VAVA, the Palestinian magazine PALESTINE AL SAURA, the Nepalese paper ASTITO, the radio of Equatorial Guinea and radio Citta Aperta of Italy. The Russian papers ROSSISKAYA PRAVDA and PATRIOT, the Egyptian paper AL TAAWON, the Peruvian paper LA REPUBLICA and the Syrian paper SYRIA TIMES carried a detailed gist of President Kim Il-song's letter to the national agricultural conference "for the ultimate solution of the rural question under the banner of the socialist rural theses."
